News.Title: Premium Plast: Muted Debut with 5% Premium on NSE SME
News.Summary: Premium Plast listed at ₹51.45 on NSE SME, a 5% premium over its IPO price of ₹49. The ₹26.20 crore SME IPO was oversubscribed 38 times. Proceeds will fund manufacturing expansion, machinery purchase, and debt repayment.

News.Title: Premium Plast: SME Debut with 19% Premium Expected
News.Summary: Premium Plast shares to list on NSE SME platform today. Grey market premium indicates a potential 19% listing gain over the IPO price of Rs 49. The company raised Rs 26.2 crore through a fresh equity issue of 53.46 lakh shares. Funds will be used for manufacturing expansion, capital expenditure, debt repayment, and general corporate purposes.
